
'''The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind''' ni filime yikinamico yo mu Bwongereza yo mu 2019 yanditswe, iyoborwa na Chiwetel Ejiofor<ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-boy-who-harnessed-the-wind-2019</ref> . Filime ishingiye kuri memoire y'izina  na William Kamkwamba na Bryan Mealer<ref>https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/307402/the-boy-who-harnessed-the-wind-by-william-kamkwamba-and-bryan-mealer-illustrated-by-elizabeth-zunon/</ref>. Yerekanwe mu gice cya Premieres mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2019 kandi itangira kunyura kuri Netflix ku ya 1 Werurwe 2019<ref>https://www.sandiego.edu/news/detail.php?_focus=71319</ref>. Yatoranijwe  muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga Yamamaye mu bihembo bya 92 bya Academy, ariko ntabwo yatowe<ref>https://www.commonsensemedia.org/movie-reviews/the-boy-who-harnessed-the-wind</ref>. 

