== Kurekurwa ==
Ku ya 14 Ugushyingo 2018, Netflix yabonye uburenganzira bwo gukwirakwiza ku isi, usibye Ubuyapani, Ubushinwa, n'Ubwongereza<ref>https://clubs.scholastic.com/the-boy-who-harnessed-the-wind%3A-young-readers-edition/9780545946032-rco-us.html</ref>.  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2019 ku ya 25 Mutarama 2019<ref>https://www.harpercollins.com/products/the-boy-who-harnessed-the-wind-william-kamkwambabryan-mealer</ref>.  Nyuma yaje gusohoka kuri Netflix ku ya 1 Werurwe 2019<ref>https://www.penguin.com.au/books/the-boy-who-harnessed-the-wind-9781984816122</ref>.

